Partnering with you

Consultants are a key source of guidance and information for retirement plan sponsors—both during the search for an investment manager or provider and after the selection. Because we share many of the same clients and have similar responsibilities, Vanguard values a strong partnership with you in serving plan sponsors and institutional investors.




Among all plan sponsor markets,Vanguard is ranked
#1 in value for cost.
                            2014 Boston Research Group Plan Sponsor Study¹




 



Your main point of contact is a relationship manager, who leads a team of professionals dedicated to serving the needs of your clients. This includes access to our extensive resources in portfolio construction, investment management, research, fiduciary and compliance matters, and data analysis.



 

 


