	Philosophy







 












         Home
      PhilosophyInvestment ApproachInvestorsContact Us


























Philosophy

Understanding and being deliberate about the risks we are taking
both at an individual stock level and at the aggregate portfolio
level lies at the core of our investment philosophy.
We invest in companies. Understanding a business, its
management, and the environment in which they operate, is
fundamental to our process.
As stewards of our investors' capital we believe it is important
to form open and close relationships with our investors; having a
limited number of clients is central to achieving this goal.












