Short description




Lancaster Investment Management is an investment group based in London and founded in 2007. Lancaster began trading in January 2008 and runs a European Fundamental Equity strategy, managed by Matthew Wood...
 We are a small team of experienced individuals and strive to create a culture where challenge and debate are expected and encouraged...
 We aim to generate investment returns that are uncorrelated with equity markets through the investment cycle, thereby allowing us to compound returns for our investors over long periods of time.














